Environment Variables:
  In order to build, the $GOROOT variable must be set as outlined in the Go documentation,
  In order to install the afp documentation, the environment variable $AFPMANDIR must be set.

Dependencies:
  - A current (>= release.2010.12.02) install of the Go compiler suite and package tree
  - ffmpeg/libavcodec/libavformat v5.1 (On debian systems `apt-get install ffmpeg libavcodec-dev libavformat-dev`) 
  - libportaudio2.0 (On debian systems `apt-get install libportaudio-dev libportaudio2`) 
  - alsa development files (On debian systems `apt-get install libasound2-dev`)
  - fftw3 libs and development files (On debian systems `apt-get install libfftw3-dev libfftw3-3`)
  - libz-dev, libbz2-dev  

Building:
  From the root of the afp source tree, issue `make`.

